<h1>Become a Volunteer!</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span8">
    <p class="lead">There are numerous way for you to join the fun</p>
    <p>
      <%= virginia_first %> relies on the help of volunteers to support all of our
      programs, assist at our events and competitions, and plan for our future. From
      administrative help and writers to field attendants and media relations, our
      volunteers have a broad spectrum of talents. VirginiaFIRST's programs,
      operations, and competitions don't happen without hundreds of people just like
      you.
    </p>
    <br>
    <p class="center">
      <%= link_to "Register for an event", volunteer_registration_path(return_to: volunteer_registration_path), class: "btn btn-large btn-success" %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="offset1 span3">
    <% event = @upcoming_events.first %>

    <% if event %>
      <h2>Next event</h2>
      <div class="<%= event.program.code %>-border">
        <h3><%= event.name %></h3>
        <p>
          <%= event.program.name %><br>
          <%= l event.starts_at, format: :date %><br>
          <%= display_location event %>
        </p>
      </div>
    <% else %>
      <p class="lead"> There are no upcoming events. Check back later. </p>

      <p>
        Are you looking for an FRC event, like the Virginia Regional? You'll need to register at
        <%= first %>'s <%= link_to "Volunteer Information & Matching System", "https://my.usfirst.org/vims/â€Ž" %>.
      </p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

